Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演算裝置？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:13.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以AIM擴散力場作為媒介構築成網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:18.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再通過複數的大腦進行處理從而使複雜代碼的演算成為可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是幻想御手的真實面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了進行某個模擬實驗而呈遞了樹形圖設計者的使用申請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:31.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼被駁回了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:34.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要能夠替代的演算裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個而對能力者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經收集了差不多一萬人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該足夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別用那麼可怕的表情看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快全部都會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:53.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大家就能解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用於卸載幻想御手的治療程序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:01.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會留下後遺癥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會恢復正常  不會犧牲任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:15.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你說這種沒有進行過充分臨床研究的東西是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是連安慰都算不上嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:19.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺嚴厲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  沒有發現木山春生的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:30.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  將數據查扣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:39.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經查到這裏了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是失去了和你的聯繫後才採取行動的話  有點太快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通過其他渠道得知的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:57.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我設置了如果不按特定的順序來啟動器材就會啟動保安系統的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來與幻想御手相關的所有數據都丟失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠喚醒其使用者的就只剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的這個程序而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真保管好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是木山春生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:33.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是只有上面下了命令的時候行動才會迅速的傢伙們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以開發幻想御手的嫌疑者將你拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻下車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？ 看來是算總帳的時候了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手是通過使用人類的大腦作為演算器的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同時  會給使用者帶來某種副產物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你看件有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把雙手放在腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後原地趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人質的少女現在很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實施逮捕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  這不是我想幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  居然是能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找錢了  請快點逃離這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山正在與警備員交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  是在使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是能力者嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在書庫的記錄當中沒有木山接受過能力開發的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很明顯是能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看起來好像是多種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力一個人只能有一種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有例外的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是幻想御手的原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:06:01.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一萬名能力者的神經突觸進行聯網的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可謂一個巨大的大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若能將其進行操控就能發生單靠人類的大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這一推測是正確的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的木山是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為不可能實現的如同幻想般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重能力者——多重能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Dual Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被全殲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因戰鬥的餘波而昏迷了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對生命沒有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園都市中僅有七人的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你也沒有碰到過像我這樣的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你  能阻止使用一萬人的大腦的我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說「能阻止嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真的能用數種能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重能力什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Dual Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:28.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力  與理論上不可能的那個的方式不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說是  多才能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,328)\fs18}Multi Skilled
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫法什麼的無關緊要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我這邊的做法是不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:47.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我不可能同時使用數種能力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:02.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧自己將自己捲進來而使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人掃興  所謂的超能力也就這種程度麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:18.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為把電擊擊破了就贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:21.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以住手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想對某件事進行調查而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個結束了就會解放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會犧牲任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會犧牲任何人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那麼多人捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄他人的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情怎麼可能放任不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…雖然是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究也只是個不諳世事的大小姐麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才沒資格說我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們每天所接受的能力開發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就認為那是安全且有人道的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:21.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市的高層隱瞞了對於能力相關的某些重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對此不明真相的教師們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日復一日地對學生的大腦進行著開發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該明白那是多麼危險的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來蠻有趣的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你之後再慢慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我調查吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空罐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  看你該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…都打飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經完…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會更難纏些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管埋怨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:45.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用磁力在瞬間形成了盾牌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零距離的電擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那個笨蛋雖然沒奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便怎樣也不會有那種不得了的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且已經手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:17.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦海裏好像直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:20.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:21.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山春生的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:29.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和木山之間通過電路連接起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我當教師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在開什麼玩笑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  你持有教師執照的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:46.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  即使拿起教鞭也不足為奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那只是順手拿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒對你說「離開研究」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:05.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此  我還想把統括理事會相當重視的實驗托付給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被稱為留精棄粗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Child Error
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:18.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為各種原因而被拋棄在學園都市的無家可歸的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是這次實驗的被試驗者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你所要任教的學生們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想讓實驗取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要取得被試驗者詳細的成長數據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:35.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加以細心的觀察並作出相應的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  讓你擔任他們的班主任不是更加省事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天起擔任你們的班主任的木山春生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計啦  中計啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  今天天氣不錯  稍微晾一下就能幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在這裏換衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生們快轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:31.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師的飛機場有什麼好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛…飛機場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是粗枝大葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:41.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師不怎麼受歡迎吧  有男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話  我來和老師交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又愛惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有什麼為難的話就告訴老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還難以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是一副很親近的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不動就纏過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  枝先
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住的公寓就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來洗個澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:45.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浴缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個浴缸值得你那麼高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在設施裏  一周只能沖兩次淋浴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:02.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以向大家炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人  要是努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠成為大能力者或是超能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現階段來說還無法下定論呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憧憬高等級的能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也有那個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我們是由學園都市撫養長大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總希望能夠為這座都市盡自己的一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究的時間全泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:21.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭…小孩子…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是喧鬧不止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗枝大葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我的女朋友好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又愛惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還難以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:46.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  祝您生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師要做還是能做到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有點疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數值上有什麼異常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裏沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裏也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是木山老師的實驗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮老師算是扮到頭了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多敏值低下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗膽堿劑沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起熱傷害低容量性衝擊更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻注射乳酸林恩凝膠液
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  繼續注射的話太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快聯絡醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:11.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌慌張張的  去好好地收集數據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對本次實驗  所裏已經下達了封口令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗已經順利告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼都沒看到  懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山  幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們有些可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:37.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是科學的發展不可避免的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把這次的事故放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:46.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還期待你今後的表現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼要做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:45.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次實驗披著「AIM擴散力場控制的實驗」的外皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:52.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實上卻是「用於解析失控能力的規律的誘爆實驗」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:57.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過刺激AIM擴散力場來探知失控的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是試驗的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:19:59.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:03.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次失控是被事先安排好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是後來才發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體…實驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們再也沒能睜開雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沉睡至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把他們當作用完就扔的小白鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  要是那樣的話  只要通報警備員…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了尋找能讓孩子們康復的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了進行事故發生原因的模擬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所申請使用樹形圖設計者的次數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有樹形圖設計者的運算能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該能夠拯救那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:52.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他們就能夠再一次在陽光下奔跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是申請被駁回了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統括理事會也是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會讓警備員出動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算這樣你也不該出此下策…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救出那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕與這座城市的所有人為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也休想讓我罷手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:29.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…網絡…失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胎兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山的野心將由我來粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學將由我來拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怪物是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人告訴我說對手是怪獸啊

